creator: STAR Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Get free pdf & practice exam oriented (SSC, BANKING and all other central and states exams) vocab in Quiz form.

- Easy to use

- You can download Free PDF of 2700+ ONE WORD SUBSTITUTIONS, 700+ PHRASAL VERBS and 600+ SPELLING CORRECTION.

- Total 23 sets are given in the app.
( EACH HAS 200 QUESTIONS)

ONE WORD SUBSTITUTIONS - 15 SET
PHRASAL VERBS - 4 SET
SPELLING CORRECTION - 4 SET

- Practice in a social media chat view QUIZ form like someone asking you questions and giving you 4 options, you have to choose correct one.

- In the result section, you will see how many Questions are correct and how many Questions are wrong as well as how many percentages are made by you. Here you can share your score with your friends.

- In the beginning MyVocabBot welcomes you and wishes you day.

- There are some jokes in the app which you can be freshen up by reading
